together and then...

10:06.155 --> 10:09.624
and then Calvin... and
he was covered in blood.

10:09.726 --> 10:11.626
And... and then he...

10:11.728 --> 10:13.394
it was... he was terrifying.

10:13.496 --> 10:15.329
Okay.

10:15.431 --> 10:17.364
