10:21.771 --> 10:24.005
That's my mother's sweater.

10:24.106 --> 10:26.273
It is.

10:26.375 --> 10:28.275
She never wears it.

10:30.079 --> 10:32.580
- It looks good on you.
- Most things do.

10:32.682 --> 10:35.282
You best clean that glass up
before your mother gets home.

10:35.384 --> 10:37.552
Yeah, I'll get right on that.

10:40.322 --> 10:44.091
So how do you fit into
this whole shit show?

10:47.030 --> 10:50.031
Your mother and your father and I

10:50.132 --> 10:51.666
go way back.

10:51.768 --> 10:53.834
Yeah? Which father?

10:55.939 --> 10:58.372
The one that gave you that smart mouth.

10:58.474 --> 10:59.473
Got it.

10:59.576 --> 11:01.576
So is she Carrie or Ana to you?

11:01.678 --> 11:04.511
