before I invented her.

11:04.614 --> 11:07.214
Well, I could use a
shiny new life myself.

11:07.316 --> 11:09.917
You want to hook me up?
I figure you owe me.

11:11.120 --> 11:13.253
Ain't you the fucked-up
little delinquent?

11:13.355 --> 11:17.424
Hey, I'm just trying to play
the shitty hand I was dealt.

11:17.526 --> 11:19.493
Girl, what you were dealt

11:19.596 --> 11:22.529
