12:10.479 --> 12:12.847
She thinks Calvin killed her father.

12:15.317 --> 12:17.284
Does Calvin know?

12:17.386 --> 12:20.187
- Does Calvin know what?
- About you two.

12:27.030 --> 12:28.763
- No.
- You sure?

12:28.865 --> 12:30.264
- Yeah.
- 'Cause you didn't think I could tell

12:30.366 --> 12:32.266
and it took me all of about
10 seconds to see it.

12:32.368 --> 12:34.434
Now, granted, I'm a
smarter than average cop

12:34.537 --> 12:36.704
- and he's a hatemongering asshole.
- Calvin doesn't know.

12:44.814 --> 12:46.613
They can stay at my place.

12:48.117 --> 12:49.516
- Really?
- Yeah.

12:49.618 --> 12:52.153
Just until you find a way
to take your brother down.

12:52.254 --> 12:54.254
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

12:56.025 --> 12:58.559
Hey, you okay, by the way?

12:58.661 --> 13:00.695
This morning, the burning.

13:00.797 --> 13:03.263
Must have hit pretty close to home?

13:05.568 --> 13:08.069
Yeah, I'm fine.

13:08.171 --> 13:12.439
Can't... get that smell out of my head.

13:14.043 --> 13:16.376
It takes a while.

13:28.467 --> 13:30.531
SUNNYSIDE CLEANERS

13:30.760 --> 13:33.460
- Can I help you?
- I highly doubt it.

13:33.562 --> 13:35.295
You can't go back there.

13:35.397 --> 13:37.732
- You can't go back there.
- I know.

13:37.834 --> 13:40.034
That's the swelling, babe.
They'll soften up...

13:40.136 --> 13:42.469
- Sweet Jesus.
- Hey, hey, you can't be in here.

13:42.571 --> 13:44.105
And yet I am. FBI.

13:44.207 --> 13:47.108
Honey, get out of here.

13:49.678 --> 13:52.113
Dr. David Quick.

13:52.215 --> 13:54.414
I have been looking for you.

13:59.922 --> 14:01.922
What's up, Doc?

14:05.161 --> 14:06.727
Why don't you take a seat?

14:06.829 --> 14:09.163
Should we try that again?

14:09.265 --> 14:10.865
Performing breast augmentation

14:10.967 --> 14:13.734
after being stripped of your medical
license, now, that's a felony.

14:13.836 --> 14:16.170
We don't perform any procedures here.
Tiffany is a friend of mine.

14:16.272 --> 14:17.972
She asked me to look at
her boob job, that's all.

14:18.074 --> 14:20.841
- So why'd you run?
- I don't like cops.

14:20.943 --> 14:23.677
Hey, you can't go in there, buddy.

14:23.780 --> 14:25.512
You got a warrant?

14:25.614 --> 14:27.581
I don't need one.

14:27.683 --> 14:29.083
I'm not a cop.

14:29.185 --> 14:31.786
Yeah, look, we can go down that road,

14:31.888 --> 14:35.890
but it's tangled and boring and
in the end, you'll still lose.

14:35.992 --> 14:38.392
Or you can answer a few questions

14:38.494 --> 14:41.862
and I'll forget we ever met.

14:42.524 --> 14:44.298
Over here.

14:45.734 --> 14:47.734
Okay.

14:47.837 --> 14:48.936
What do you want to know?

14:49.038 --> 14:51.038
- Body modifications.
- What about it?

14:51.140 --> 14:53.207
- You do it?
- Now and then. It's a growing field.

14:53.309 --> 14:54.909
So you must do some
pretty fucked-up shit.

14:55.011 --> 14:57.044
Not as fucked up as
the shit I turn down.

14:57.146 --> 14:59.280
You wouldn't believe the
kind of things people want.

14:59.381 --> 15:02.183
Hey, Jesus, man!

15:02.285 --> 15:03.550
Shit's expensive.

15:03.652 --> 15:05.419
I'm looking for a guy
with horn implants.

15:05.521 --> 15:07.754
- You ever do anything like that?
- Yeah.

15:07.857 --> 15:10.257
Well, then whip out your files, Doc.

15:10.359 --> 15:13.760
