15:21.137 --> 15:23.103
Yeah, but still, it's pretty unique,

15:23.206 --> 15:24.571
even for a guy like you.

15:24.673 --> 15:26.040
Who was the last guy you did?

15:26.142 --> 15:27.441
I'm sure you remember something.

15:27.543 --> 15:29.576
The kind of people who want this shit,

15:29.678 --> 15:31.378
