15:31.480 --> 15:34.048
I take cash in advance. I
don't even ask their names.

15:34.150 --> 15:36.516
How convenient for you.

15:36.618 --> 15:38.118
This is bullshit.

15:38.221 --> 15:39.586
I'm gonna call my lawyer.

15:39.688 --> 15:41.521
Let's go.

15:41.623 --> 15:43.224
He doesn't know anything.

15:48.898 --> 15:53.767
This has not been a satisfying
conversation for me, Dr. Quick.

15:53.870 --> 15:56.971
If I were you, I'd call me.

15:58.407 --> 16:00.607
Thank you.

16:02.245 --> 16:04.144
I barely started working that guy.

16:04.247 --> 16:05.746
He wasn't gonna talk.

16:05.848 --> 16:07.414
This might help.

16:07.516 --> 16:09.250
That was on his desk.

16:10.719 --> 16:12.786
You, my friend, have
some serious skills.

16:12.889 --> 16:14.621
He was watching you the
whole time, so was I.

16:14.723 --> 16:16.757
- How'd you do it?
- That's the trick, isn't it?

16:18.660 --> 16:21.061
Just when I thought I'd seen it all.

16:22.865 --> 16:27.902
Wow, amazing what low self-esteem
can do to a sociopath.

16:35.601 --> 16:38.601
