16:49.926 --> 16:51.858
remember that matter you
asked me to look into?

16:51.961 --> 16:54.395
- Yeah.
- I looked into it.

16:54.496 --> 16:55.896
You found him?

16:55.998 --> 16:58.132
No, I found her.

16:58.234 --> 17:00.100
Exhibit number four was also turned in

17:00.202 --> 17:04.338
to our hearing officer five
days before this trial began.

17:04.440 --> 17:06.606
Now, if it pleases the court,
you'll note that the photograph

17:06.708 --> 17:09.709
shows the remnants of a
crushed back side door.

17:09.811 --> 17:12.846
- This photograph was taken at
the scene... - Mrs. Hopewell.

17:12.949 --> 17:15.983
...of a hit-and-run five months
back at the intersection...

17:16.085 --> 17:20.220
I'm seeing you around the
courthouse quite often these days.

17:20.323 --> 17:23.589
Taking an interest in the law?

17:23.692 --> 17:26.193
You could say that.

17:29.165 --> 17:31.731
You know, I never really had the chance

17:31.834 --> 17:35.302
