the loss of your husband.

17:37.239 --> 17:39.006
You hated Gordon.

17:39.108 --> 17:42.109
No, didn't hate him.

17:42.211 --> 17:43.777
I respected him.

17:43.879 --> 17:46.213
I never took it personally.

17:46.315 --> 17:48.482
I'd like to think he didn't either.

17:52.688 --> 17:54.621
He did.

17:57.826 --> 18:02.496
Well, either way, I was very
sorry to hear about it.

18:07.203 --> 18:09.336
I'm sorry about your niece.

18:11.073 --> 18:14.174
We both suffered a great loss.

18:15.844 --> 18:19.146
You know, sometimes a loss like that

18:19.248 --> 18:21.348
