18:26.722 --> 18:28.288
Things we might regret.

18:28.391 --> 18:30.590
Do you know what I mean?

18:32.261 --> 18:34.328
No, not really.

18:34.430 --> 18:38.832
No? Well, I'd watch out for it.

18:38.934 --> 18:40.967
You still have so much to lose.

18:44.940 --> 18:47.074
I guess we all do.

18:51.280 --> 18:54.214
I suppose we both
should be more careful.

19:21.977 --> 19:23.643
Remember me, sunshine?

19:23.745 --> 19:26.080
Yeah, the bitch who didn't know
when to stop asking questions.

19:26.182 --> 19:28.848
You remembered. I'm so flattered.

19:28.951 --> 19:30.617
