19:30.719 --> 19:32.719
Did I not mention that the other day?

19:32.821 --> 19:35.355
- I don't want any trouble, all right?
- Now that's the spirit.

19:35.458 --> 19:37.591
We're looking for a
guy with devil horns.

19:37.693 --> 19:40.561
