20:16.365 --> 20:18.365
- Where do we find him?
- Fuck if I know.

20:18.467 --> 20:20.867
- You knew his name. - Yeah, and
that's all I'm telling you, cop.

20:20.969 --> 20:23.036
- Where do we fucking find him?!
- I don't fucking know, man.

20:23.139 --> 20:24.671
- Where?!
- I don't fucking know.

20:24.773 --> 20:27.807
The fucking guy thinks the Devil
works through him, all right?

20:27.909 --> 20:29.610
One night the freak comes in here,

20:29.711 --> 20:31.612
starts spouting off about how
he's talking to Lucifer.

20:31.713 --> 20:34.714
I tell him he's full of shit. Guy takes
the paring knife out of my hand,

20:34.816 --> 20:36.983
starts peeling back his
fingernails one by one,

20:37.085 --> 20:38.718
smiling the whole time.

20:38.820 --> 20:42.289
