Who the fuck does that?

20:42.391 --> 20:43.923
Someone we should meet.

20:44.026 --> 20:47.694
See? When we're helping, we're happy.

21:51.993 --> 21:55.362
Yeah? Well, that's interesting.

21:55.464 --> 21:56.896
Okay.

21:56.998 --> 21:59.399
All right, thanks. I'll call you back.

22:01.437 --> 22:04.638
Our boy Declan Bode doesn't
have much of a footprint.

22:04.740 --> 22:06.607
No known address. No relatives.

22:06.709 --> 22:08.242
