the federal judges.

22:30.098 --> 22:32.198
All right, so what do we do now?

22:32.301 --> 22:34.100
Now we wait.

22:35.937 --> 22:37.738
Just wait?

22:37.839 --> 22:39.473
Yeah.

22:40.457 --> 22:41.675
Great.

22:50.051 --> 22:54.187
You're not built for downtime, are you?

22:54.290 --> 22:56.456
The way you move, the way you pace,

22:56.558 --> 22:58.258
the way you want to
push through every wall

22:58.360 --> 23:01.027
without even looking for the
door or the key to that door.

23:01.129 --> 23:02.562
You have a point?

23:02.665 --> 23:04.097
That's not the temperament of a man

23:04.199 --> 23:05.865
