23:39.000 --> 23:41.167
You've got a secret.

23:41.269 --> 23:43.670
Or secrets.

23:44.940 --> 23:47.240
Maybe I just don't like you.

23:48.761 --> 23:50.910
But you do.

23:51.012 --> 23:52.846
Don't you?

23:56.385 --> 23:58.918
You think you know me?

23:59.020 --> 24:02.389
Let me tell you something.
You have no fucking idea.

24:03.925 --> 24:06.526
Yeah, I check the corners because
for as long as I can remember,

24:06.628 --> 24:09.128
