24:27.182 --> 24:30.149
No, I'm not.

25:38.219 --> 25:40.053
It's nothing.

26:03.846 --> 26:05.745
Hey.

26:07.816 --> 26:09.816
What is it?

26:13.689 --> 26:15.822
