28:24.786 --> 28:28.688
- Is that so?
- Yes, that is so.

28:30.358 --> 28:32.826
Well, that's unfortunate.

28:32.928 --> 28:36.062
Not from where I'm sitting.

28:37.699 --> 28:41.034
I can't help but wonder what
Watts will think about this.

28:43.905 --> 28:46.305
Well, why don't we ask him?

28:50.612 --> 28:53.179
What do you think, Randall?

28:53.281 --> 28:56.116
Seems the cat got Watts's tongue.

28:56.217 --> 28:57.951
That's a bold choice.

28:58.053 --> 29:00.553
Yeah.

29:00.656 --> 29:02.822
I thought you'd like that.

29:10.298 --> 29:12.598
So here's how it's gonna work.

29:12.668 --> 29:14.333
Everything that's yours is now ours.

29:14.435 --> 29:18.271
Warehouses, shipments, buyers,
I fucking want all of it.

29:18.373 --> 29:21.240
You can go quietly or you can go bloody,

29:21.342 --> 29:23.109
but either way you are gone.

29:31.019 --> 29:33.519
You can keep the head as a souvenir.

30:02.851 --> 30:04.751
Hi.

30:04.853 --> 30:07.087
I saw you on TV.

30:07.189 --> 30:10.523
I didn't ask for this.

30:10.625 --> 30:12.558
He chose me.

30:12.660 --> 30:14.493
Do you understand?

30:14.596 --> 30:16.796
He chose me.

30:16.898 --> 30:19.298
You can't stop me.

30:19.400 --> 30:22.335
I've been delivered.

30:22.437 --> 30:25.205
To feed the beast,

30:25.306 --> 30:29.508
