different, something more.

30:29.611 --> 30:32.411
And you, you're a bug.

30:32.513 --> 30:35.982
A tiny, worthless insect
in the face of his power.

30:36.084 --> 30:37.951
Fuck you.

30:39.755 --> 30:41.621
Close your eyes, cop.

30:41.723 --> 30:43.589
Close your eyes.

30:43.691 --> 30:45.591
Cherish the darkness,

30:45.693 --> 30:48.561
for soon you will bear
witness to his plan.

30:48.663 --> 30:50.696
And only then

30:50.799 --> 30:54.934
will I take your miserable little life.

31:24.232 --> 31:25.198
Where are they, Kurt?

31:25.300 --> 31:27.700
Get the fuck off my property.

31:28.703 --> 31:30.403
Where's my wife?!

31:31.907 --> 31:33.173
She's somewhere safe.

31:33.275 --> 31:35.141
She'll call you when she's ready.

31:35.243 --> 31:38.778
You are fucking with my family, Kurt.

31:38.880 --> 31:41.281
My wife, my son.

31:41.382 --> 31:44.818
Do you have any idea what I will
fucking do to you for that?

31:46.054 --> 31:48.154
Where's Watts?

31:50.258 --> 31:52.292
Watts is dead.

31:52.393 --> 31:53.759
Where's Maggie?

31:53.862 --> 31:55.695
She doesn't want to see you.

31:55.797 --> 31:58.497
Fuck you. You don't get
to fucking tell me that.

31:58.599 --> 32:01.434
I just did. I'm going into my house.

32:01.536 --> 32:04.403
In two minutes, if you're still here,

32:04.505 --> 32:06.372
I'll come back out.

32:06.474 --> 32:11.010
Trust me, you don't want
me to come back out.

32:17.152 --> 32:18.718
Kurt.

32:22.590 --> 32:24.958
Do you remember Dad used to take us

32:25.060 --> 32:27.426
to the dogfights over in Vandergrift?

32:30.698 --> 32:31.664
Yeah.

32:31.766 --> 32:34.533
I remember I once asked him...

32:36.171 --> 32:38.872
if the matches ever ended in a tie.

32:41.243 --> 32:45.245
And he laughed at me

32:45.347 --> 32:47.847
and he said,

32:47.949 --> 32:51.384
"There's only ever one way
that a dogfight ends."

32:55.490 --> 32:57.456
You remember that?

33:02.364 --> 33:04.264
Yeah, I remember.

33:12.173 --> 33:14.507
There's only one way, Kurt.

33:20.282 --> 33:22.081
I know.

34:43.164 --> 34:45.398
Deva!

35:06.654 --> 35:08.454
- Are you hurt?
- No.

35:09.857 --> 35:11.891
Come on. Come on.

35:11.993 --> 35:13.526
Get out there. Get on the roof.

35:13.628 --> 35:15.495
- What?
- Go, go, go!

35:15.596 --> 35:17.763
Here, take this. Safety's off.

35:17.865 --> 35:20.633
Two hands. Point and squeeze.

35:20.735 --> 35:23.169
Find a place to hide, wait.
You stay safe.

35:24.243 --> 35:25.204
Go.

35:25.306 --> 35:27.373
Now!

38:01.563 --> 38:03.729
No.

39:01.522 --> 39:06.024
I am sick and tired...

39:06.127 --> 39:09.395
...of fighting for my
motherfucking life.

39:16.704 --> 39:17.670
Damn.

39:21.342 --> 39:22.375
Where's Deva?

39:27.782 --> 39:29.948
Deva.

39:31.018 --> 39:32.685
Are you hurt?

39:32.787 --> 39:35.388
Give me this.

39:39.026 --> 39:40.726
I'm sorry.

39:40.828 --> 39:43.663
I'm sorry.

39:50.438 --> 39:52.171
I'm sorry.

39:53.974 --> 39:55.474
I'm sorry.

40:11.726 --> 40:13.526
Deva.

40:15.823 --> 40:17.663
Slow down. Slow down.

40:37.752 --> 40:40.353
You okay? You hurt?

40:46.761 --> 40:48.126
Okay.

40:48.229 --> 40:50.195
I just want to go home.

40:52.467 --> 40:53.699
I know.

40:53.801 --> 40:56.535
The thing is, I don't
know where that is.

40:58.706 --> 41:00.706
Come here.

41:26.367 --> 41:28.267
Underwood, tell me you have something.

41:28.335 --> 41:29.935
The judge unsealed the file.

41:30.037 --> 41:32.805
The victim on that statutory
rape is a Kim Newton.

41:32.907 --> 41:34.440
She still lives in the area.

41:34.542 --> 41:36.942
- You got an address?
- Just emailed it to you.

41:37.044 --> 41:39.144
You're the best. I owe you.

41:39.246 --> 41:41.514
You owe me many.

41:43.350 --> 41:45.117
What is it with this fucking town?

41:45.219 --> 41:49.087
Can't we go one week without some
motherfucking army shooting at us?

41:49.189 --> 41:51.056
Seems like you handled it fine.

41:51.158 --> 41:54.493
That's because it's already
become a motherfucking habit.

41:57.264 --> 41:59.097
Thank you.

42:04.472 --> 42:07.072
Baby, there's a whole world out there.

42:07.174 --> 42:09.141
So they tell me.

42:20.120 --> 42:22.120
What the fuck happened here?

42:24.759 --> 42:25.991
Proctor.

42:26.093 --> 42:28.327
What are you doing messing with him?

42:28.429 --> 42:31.363
Are you kidding me?

42:31.466 --> 42:34.533
You don't get to walk into my life
every few years and question me.

42:34.635 --> 42:37.503
Hey, hey, Deva could have
been fucking killed.

42:38.606 --> 42:40.506
Get out of here.

42:40.608 --> 42:43.275
- Come on, Ana.
- Get the fuck out of here!

42:43.377 --> 42:45.143
Who the fuck do you think you
are saying that shit to me?!

42:45.245 --> 42:47.112
Do you think I don't know what
could have happened there?!

42:47.214 --> 42:48.681
You think I don't know what...

42:49.602 --> 42:51.550
Hey, hey, stop.

42:51.652 --> 42:54.052
It's okay.

42:54.154 --> 42:56.054
It's okay.

42:59.326 --> 43:01.126
It's okay.

43:01.228 --> 43:03.028
It's okay.

43:24.652 --> 43:26.952
Hello. Can I help you?

43:27.054 --> 43:28.854
Kim Newton?

43:28.956 --> 43:30.589
Yes.

43:31.759 --> 43:35.060
My parents were the ones
that called the police.

43:35.162 --> 43:38.497
I was 15, Declan, he was 25.

43:38.599 --> 43:41.600
I was a quiet girl.

43:41.702 --> 43:44.102
You know, I didn't have
many friends in school.

43:44.204 --> 43:46.338
Always the kid in the back row.

43:46.440 --> 43:49.608
Nobody really paid any attention to me.

43:49.710 --> 43:52.878
And then I met Declan.

43:52.980 --> 43:56.381
He told me I was beautiful and
I could tell he meant it.

43:56.483 --> 43:59.084
I had never even been kissed before

43:59.186 --> 44:02.287
and here was this handsome older guy

44:02.389 --> 44:04.023
falling head over heels in love with me.

44:04.124 --> 44:07.259
And I understand now that I
was young and impressionable

44:07.361 --> 44:11.263
and he manipulated me, but, you know...

44:12.900 --> 44:15.467
I still think he loved me

44:15.570 --> 44:18.437
and I know I loved him.

44:20.841 --> 44:22.041
So what happened?

44:22.142 --> 44:23.475
My dad found out.

44:23.578 --> 44:26.645
He wanted to go after
Declan with a tire iron,

44:26.747 --> 44:31.116
but my mother convinced him
to call the police instead.

44:32.186 --> 44:34.987
Oh, I cried for days.

44:36.991 --> 44:38.924
And the sex?

44:39.026 --> 44:42.194
Was it perverse in any way?

44:42.296 --> 44:45.064
It was intense, but, no,

44:45.165 --> 44:47.900
I wouldn't say it was perverse.

44:49.172 --> 44:51.637
Is Declan in some kind of trouble?

44:51.706 --> 44:53.205
He's a person of interest.

44:53.307 --> 44:57.109
When was the last time you spoke to him?

44:57.211 --> 44:58.811
The night he was arrested.

44:58.913 --> 45:02.147
After that, I never saw him again.

45:14.595 --> 45:16.662
It's a nice piece of property you have.

45:16.764 --> 45:20.298
Oh, thanks. My parents left it to me.

45:22.637 --> 45:24.603
Well, if you think of anything else,

45:24.705 --> 45:26.271
give me a call.

45:26.340 --> 45:28.206
- Thanks for your time.
- Yeah.

45:57.672 --> 45:59.738
Hey, it's Veronica.

45:59.840 --> 46:02.507
You disappeared on me this morning.

46:02.609 --> 46:06.444
But, anyway, I tracked down
our statutory rape victim.

46:06.547 --> 46:08.180
She said all the right things,

46:08.282 --> 46:10.716
but my bullshit meter is ringing.

46:10.818 --> 46:13.451
Anyway, I'm going back to the hotel,

46:13.554 --> 46:16.612
so call me and I'll fill you in on my...

46:38.612 --> 46:40.713
Oh, shit.

